{"word":"崖","detail":[{"title":"基本字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"● "},{"type":"strong","content":"崖"},{"type":"span","content":"yáㄧㄚˊ","class":["pinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 高地的边，陡立的山边：山"},{"type":"span","content":"崖","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"。悬"},{"type":"span","content":"崖","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"。"},{"type":"span","content":"崖","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"谷。"},{"type":"span","content":"崖","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"壑。"},{"type":"span","content":"崖","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"壁。"},{"type":"span","content":"崖","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"葬（悬棺葬）。"},{"type":"span","content":"崖","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"岸。悬"},{"type":"span","content":"崖","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"勒马。"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎ 边际："},{"type":"span","content":"崖","class":["fontred"]},{"type":"text","content":"略（大略，梗概）。"}]]},{"title":"英文翻译","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"cliff, precipice; precipitous"}]]},{"title":"详细字义解释","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"崖"},{"type":"text","content":" 崕、厓 "},{"type":"span","content":"yá","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"span","content":"〈名词〉","class":["parts"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"(1)  (形声。从山,厓( "},{"type":"span","content":"yá","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" )声。本义:岸;水边)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(2) 同本义"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"崖,高边也。——《说文》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"崖,岸。高边也。…此云高边,崖则水之边而峭高者也。——《说文句读》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"渊生珠而崖不枯。——《荀子·劝学》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"望厓洒而高岸。——《尔雅·释丘》。按:“厓之峻而高者,岸也,即岸也。”"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"伯有廷劳于黄崖。——《左传·襄公二十八年》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"泾流之大,两涘渚崖之间,不辨牛马。——《庄子·秋水》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"君其涉于江而浮于海,望之而不见其崖。——《庄子·山水》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"穹崖巨谷。——宋·沈括《梦溪笔谈》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"蹑履登崖。——明·刘基《诚意伯刘文成公文集》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"石崖侧削。——《徐霞客游记·游黄山记》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"四眺重崖,皆悬绝无径,而西崖尤为峻峭。——《徐霞客游记》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(3) 又如:崖谷(悬崖深谷);崖口(山崖间的豁口);崖垠(山崖的边际);崖畔(山崖边);崖岭(高崖峻岭);崖穴(山洞)"}],[{"type":"text","content":"(4) 泛指事物的边际;界域。如:崖际(边际)"}]]},{"title":"词性变化","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎ "},{"type":"strong","content":"崖"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"yá","class":["pinyin"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"img","content":"","class":["sound"]},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"span","content":"〈形容词〉","class":["parts"]},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"言人性格孤高。如:崖异(乖异。指人性情、言行不合常理);崖然(傲岸矜持的样子)"}]]},{"title":"常用词组","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"崖壁"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"yábì","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"山崖的陡立面"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"崖谷"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"yágǔ","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"山崖"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"崖壑"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"yáhè","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"高崖深谷"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"崖略"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"yálüè","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"大略;概略;梗概"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"将为汝言其崖略。——《庄子·知北游》"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"颇能知其崖略。——清·黄宗羲《再答忍阉宗兄》"}],[{"type":"text","content":"◎  "},{"type":"strong","content":"崖限"},{"type":"text","content":" "},{"type":"span","content":"yáxiàn","class":["cpinyin"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"像门槛一样挡在路上的山崖"},{"type":"br","content":""},{"type":"text","content":"崖限当道者。——清·姚鼐《登泰山记》"}]]},{"title":"康熙字典","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【寅集中】【山字部】崖 ·康熙筆画：11　·部外筆画：8 "}],[{"type":"text","content":"【集韻】【韻會】【正韻】"},{"type":"span","content":"𠀤"},{"type":"text","content":"宜佳切，音睚。【說文】高邊也。从屵，圭聲。【徐曰】水邊有垠堮也。無垠堮而平曰汀。【郭璞·江賦】觸曲崖以縈繞。　又珠崖，郡名。在南海，漢武帝置，地居海中，產珠，故曰珠崖，亦曰朱崖。　又洪崖，仙人名。【郭璞·遊仙詩】右拍洪崖肩。　又不和物曰崖岸。宋張詠性剛介，自號乖崖，言乖則違衆，崖不和物也。　又【集韻】魚羈切【韻會】疑羈切，"},{"type":"span","content":"𠀤"},{"type":"text","content":"音儀，義同。○按《說文》厂部厓訓山邊，屵部崖訓高邊，分厓崖爲二，韻會因之，以山邊屬睚音，高邊屬儀音，似泥。"}]]},{"title":"说文解字","content":[[{"type":"text","content":"【卷九】【屵部】"},{"type":"span","content":"崖","class":["kszi"]}],[{"type":"text","content":"高邊也。从屵圭聲。五佳切"}]]},{"title":"字源演变","content":[]},{"title":"同音字","content":[]}],"type":"通用字、常用字","pinyin":["yá","ái"],"radical":"山","stroke":"八画","total_stroke":"十一画","stroke_order":"丨フ丨一ノ一丨一一丨一","input_method":{"bopomofo":"UMGG","number":"22214","unicode":"U+5D16","wubi":"MDFF"}}